    "description": "《伪信号 - FAKE SIGNALS》是一款轻度动作肉鸽游戏。潜入敌方营地，用各种武器来一场花式击杀秀吧！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2161430/extras/36a3c5957e2211ba56784bd508205d9a.poster.avif?t=1749785241\" width=600 height=160 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2161430/extras/36a3c5957e2211ba56784bd508205d9a.webm?t=1749785241\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2161430/extras/36a3c5957e2211ba56784bd508205d9a.mp4?t=1749785241\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏特色</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>3大特色主题场景，27项不同任务。<br></li><li>超过20种武器可供使用。<br></li><li>场景物品支持互动，为挑战创造更多可能。<br></li><li>敌人类型丰富，同时装备各种武器。<br></li><li>赚取金币解锁导航应用。<br></li><li>不必畏惧死亡，复仇的时刻转瞬即至。</li></ul><br>利用各种近战、远程、投掷、陷阱、爆炸武器来灵活杀敌。<br>不同的武器和不同的路线选择将带给你迥然各异的游戏体验。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2161430/extras/84ba405c72aa7bfaec45ee13883319da.poster.avif?t=1749785241\" width=600 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2161430/extras/84ba405c72aa7bfaec45ee13883319da.webm?t=1749785241\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2161430/extras/84ba405c72aa7bfaec45ee13883319da.mp4?t=1749785241\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>注意寻找掩体，获取藏在其中的武器。<br>关闭灯光，黑暗中的你更有优势。<br>控制电梯移动，把握开关门时机，巧妙利用各种互动要素来完成任务。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2161430/extras/998ac5e02eb988456a65543f50803b9c.poster.avif?t=1749785241\" width=600 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2161430/extras/998ac5e02eb988456a65543f50803b9c.webm?t=1749785241\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2161430/extras/998ac5e02eb988456a65543f50803b9c.mp4?t=1749785241\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>车载导航中的各种信息将协助你通过考验。<br>你可以在车载导航中查看关卡、武器、邮件、音乐等多种信息。<br>部分导航应用需要金币解锁。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2161430/extras/a2f83209aa889c080905b9c8cbdbbb0c.poster.avif?t=1749785241\" width=600 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2161430/extras/a2f83209aa889c080905b9c8cbdbbb0c.webm?t=1749785241\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2161430/extras/a2f83209aa889c080905b9c8cbdbbb0c.mp4?t=1749785241\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>希望您在游戏中玩得开心！<br>想了解更多关于FAKE SIGNALS的信息，请加入官方Discord频道。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2161430/extras/260567face0421b509f7fae1584740fd.poster.avif?t=1749785241\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2161430/extras/260567face0421b509f7fae1584740fd.webm?t=1749785241\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2161430/extras/260567face0421b509f7fae1584740fd.mp4?t=1749785241\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
